  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><p>Please download today&#39;s hiragana practice here: <a class=\"fr-file\" href=\"../../pdfs/week_02/day_08/Hiragana_Practice_Day_8.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Hiragana Practice Day 8.pdf</a></p><p>Practising writing hiragana every day is a very important exercise to help you learn quickly. If you have any questions you can always ask other students and teachers in the community <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/communities/Q29tbXVuaXR5LTM1MzQ=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p><p>To learn and practice the long sound vowels (ちょうおん) you can watch this free YouTube tutorial:<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hFbsWVMCgJM?t=233\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"></a><br><a href=\"https://youtu.be/SLP1BxU6AR4\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SLP1BxU6AR4</a></p></div>",
